```java
// 创建DataSource实例
DataSource dataSource = new UnpooledDataSource("org.hsqldb.jdbcDriver","jdbc:hsqldb:mem:mybatis","sa", "");
// 获取Connection对象
Connection connection = dataSource.getConnection();
```
